      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped mango</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>and <strong>chopped green chilli</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>lime zest</strong> with the juice of <strong>half </strong>your<strong> lime[s]</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and toss together – this is your <strong>mango & lime salad</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p><p>Combine the <strong>softened butter</strong> with your<strong> jerk paste</strong> – this is your <strong>jerk butter</strong></p>",
