    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, add the<strong> chopped creamed coconut </strong>and <strong>drained black beans</strong> to the pot with 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [85ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cover with a lid and cook over a low heat, stirring occasionally, for 7-8 min or until the coconut has melted and the water has absorbed – this is your <strong>coconut rice</strong></p>",
